TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {18102=The day preceding the Forum, on Monday June 3, the leaders of GA member associations will gather at the ProCom Office in Helsinki to join the Association Leaders’ Meeting and the GA Annual General Meeting. During the meeting, common challenges and opportunities in association management will be shared. More information on the theme and the agenda will be available soon., 17094=The Global Alliance for Public Relations and Communication Management will hold its Annual Meeting and Nordic, Baltic and Russian PR Leadership Forum in Helsinki, Finland on June 3-4, 2013.}
